- Description:
A natural resource obtained through Gathering that can be used as an ingredient in Alchemy and Cooking.
- How to Obtain: Bluffer Mushrooms can be Gathered using Bare Hands or a Hoe.

 ※ Consuming this item without Cooking will grant a special buff, but you may be poisoned!

Mushrooms have long been called “the food from the earth” or “the incarnation of fairies”. Some of them are even poisonous. They also have unique chemical properties, which is why they are commonly used in Alchemy. The Bluffer Mushroom can be cultivated in your garden if you have its hypha.
